name: Astro Vamp
description: This “Astro Vamp” is a rotoscope animation test (2012), you’ll notice some behind the scenes clips in the loop as well. I was working towards a more stylized "60's/70's" aesthetic, trying to nail it down to something inspired by the 1967 Spider-Man cartoon or vintage Ralph Bakshi animation style. Yes, that's a soccer ball on my head!
